headline: Why Are Hillenbrand (HI) Shares Soaring Today
summary: Shares of industrial processing equipment and solutions provider Hillenbrand (NYSE:HI) jumped 9.1% in the afternoon session after reports indicated the company was nearing the final stages of its sale process, with final bids expected in the following week.
